    "    <h1 style=\"color: #2F4F4F; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">Frenado Rotacional de un Púlsar</h1>\n",
    "    <p style=\"color: #2F4F4F; font-family: Calibri, Courier, monospace; text-align: center; font-size: 24px;\">\n",
    "        \n",
    "</div>\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
